dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Bayfield County, WI 2021
dc_description_s: This data represents roads and right of way (ROW) for Bayfield County in 2021. [For Roads: This layer contains road centerline data in Bayfield County. For ROW: This layer contains ROW polyline data for right-of-way areas in Bayfield County. Link to metadata information: https://www.bayfieldcounty.org/437/GIS-Metadata]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: [https://www.bayfieldcounty.org/892/GIS-Data-Download]
